As I grew older my love for minimal jewellery  increased ✨

@limelightdiamonds has an amazing collection of minimal jewellery and they bring you the Dream Dazzle Collection - The Affordable Edit, featuring diamond jewellery studded with the purest lab-grown CVD diamonds. 💎 

Interestingly, these are eco-friendly diamonds that are absolutely real but at the same time planet friendly because they are not mined but instead grown above in labs in exactly the same way. So they end up saving huge tonnes of land and gallons of water that is destroyed in mining - something that is so critical in current times where our environment & planet needs our attention and care.
Amazing, right? 

Go check out their collection to get yours.
